title: Jenkins and Jonez - Steph Curry is Shooting His Way To Top 10 All Time
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Steph Curry is Shooting His Way To Top 10 All Time
description:
The guys discuss the video of Steph Curry pointing at a fan before his shot went in (1:30), the stupidity of NBA tampering investigations (8:00), and then do a Booger Boy of the Week-off to see who is the boogeriest (12:00).
